{"tid":833539,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大學生說“不愛國” 學校稱其“辱國”取消學籍","createTime":"2018-09-23T14:54:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-24T02:45:21.000Z","uid":184679,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"bf29ea46de1f1c31d9da284f507470c85d8e7ee2","tid":833539,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T14:54:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://scd.cn.rfi.fr/sites/chinese.filesrfi/dynimagecache/0/142/440/248/600/338/sites/images.rfi.fr/files/aef_image/3s9f-hkmwytn6539165.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fscd.cn.rfi.fr%2Fsites%2Fchinese.filesrfi%2Fdynimagecache%2F0%2F142%2F440%2F248%2F600%2F338%2Fsites%2Fimages.rfi.fr%2Ffiles%2Faef_image%2F3s9f-hkmwytn6539165.jpg&h=8c343cf6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最近一名網名為&ldquo;貴州省省草王英俊&rdquo;的大一新生王棟在微博上表示，&ldquo;一輩子都不可能愛國&rdquo;、&ldquo;都他媽大學生了還愛國&rdquo;，遭網民舉報後，這名學生就讀的湖南城市學院稱其言論&ldquo;辱國&rdquo;隨後將他退學。<br />\n<br />\n中央社報道，湖南城市學院22日在官網發布&ldquo;關於取消土木院新生王棟入學資格的情況通報&rdquo;指出，王姓學生在網路發布&ldquo;辱國言論&rdquo;遭到網友舉報。 通報指出，王姓學生在微博以&ldquo;貴州省省草王英俊&rdquo;為名，發表&ldquo;愛國是不可能愛國的，老子一輩子都不可能愛國、都他媽大學生了還愛國，我看你就是蠢貨&rdquo;等&ldquo;辱國言論&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n有關部門和學校確認網名&ldquo;貴州省省草王英俊&rdquo;是新生王棟，王棟也承認。又查，自9月9日入學以來，王棟多次在學生宿舍發表&ldquo;辱國言論&rdquo;，且不聽同學勸阻，並對同室同學愛國言論冷嘲熱諷。<br />\n<br />\n通報說，鑒於王棟散布&ldquo;辱國等極其錯誤言論，影響極壞&rdquo;，經學校校長辦公會研究《國家招生考試規定》及《湖南省2018年普通高等學校招生工作實施辦法》有關條款各項規定後，決定取消王棟入學資格。<br />\n<br />\n這份通報最後宣示，將深入貫徹中國全國教育大會精神，堅決反對&ldquo;損害黨和國家聲譽&ldquo;的言行，全面貫徹黨（中共）的教育方針，切實加強思想政治工作，堅持立德樹人，在全校師生員工中深入展開社會主義核心價值觀教育，&rdquo;引導全校師生堅定四個自信，增強四個意識，愛黨愛國愛人民，為培養擔當民族復興大任的時代新人而努力。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.trad.cn.rfi.fr/中國/20180923-大學生說不愛國-學校稱其辱國取消學籍\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.trad.cn.rfi.fr%2F%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%2F20180923-%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E8%AA%AA%E4%B8%8D%E6%84%9B%E5%9C%8B-%E5%AD%B8%E6%A0%A1%E7%A8%B1%E5%85%B6%E8%BE%B1%E5%9C%8B%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88%E5%AD%B8%E7%B1%8D&d=YiQ0ngMPxCLw3zTHWrzy76NGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=aad94c4a\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.trad.cn.rfi.fr/中國/20180923-大學生說不愛國-學校稱其辱國取消學籍</a>"},{"pid":"f652ae8706eec78cf5fd45a8c2ebc9d96344706b","tid":833539,"uid":144626,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T14:55:26.000Z","msg":"我係呢條友立即考IELTS然後考外國d大學<br />\n此地不宜久留呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab653695e24c3df17c512805e58bb18f6b0be2f2","tid":833539,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T14:56:32.000Z","msg":"遲早到香港"},{"pid":"5fe6f814556599b92cb5b59a652b80750a6293fa","tid":833539,"uid":81424,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"f652ae8706eec78cf5fd45a8c2ebc9d96344706b","tid":833539,"uid":144626,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T14:55:26.000Z","msg":"我係呢條友立即考IELTS然後考外國d大學<br />\n此地不宜久留呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T14:57:51.000Z","msg":"佢鳩噏多幾句然後直接申請政治庇護易啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abe2e39cf16e0286f9e43bfd23028013d05a50bc","tid":833539,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5fe6f814556599b92cb5b59a652b80750a6293fa","tid":833539,"uid":81424,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"f652ae8706eec78cf5fd45a8c2ebc9d96344706b","tid":833539,"uid":144626,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T14:55:26.000Z","msg":"我係呢條友立即考IELTS然後考外國d大學<br />\n此地不宜久留呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T14:57:51.000Z","msg":"佢鳩噏多幾句然後直接申請政治庇護易啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T15:01:04.000Z","msg":"都得，條條大路通歐美<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/ag